'''Arrow Books''' is an [[Wikipedia:imprint|imprint]] of [[Random House]] Publishers Group. They are responsible for Random House's paperback ''[[Star Wars]]'' fiction publications in the [[Wikipedia:United Kingdom|United Kingdom]], [[Wikipedia:Australia|Australia]] and [[Wikipedia:New Zealand|New Zealand]]. Hardback publications are handled by [[Century (Random House)|Century]], and factual books (such as ''[[The Making of Star Wars Revenge of the Sith]]'') are published under the [[Ebury Press]] label.

